\": 730, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_technology\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintech\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_technology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_technology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knowing the secrets of producing interesting and creative content, Flam has transformed traditional print advertisements into dynamic, interactive experiences that can surely appeal to the targeted audience.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This partnership unambiguously establishes Flam as a key market participant in mixed reality and demonstrates the company's versatility in adapting to the demands of various sectors.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Flam has consistently pushed the boundaries of interactive advertising, delivering captivating experiences for brands like Britannia, Samsung, and AJIO, to name a few across various spheres such as F&B, Consumer Electronics, E-commerce, Real Estate, and more.\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britannia\", \"score\": 0.996004788416998, \"rank\": 0.002873369809975708, \"text\": \"Britannia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britannia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Britannia\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.999998698405699, \"rank\": 1.3015937853763287e-06, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodservice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"F&B\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodservice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodservice\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With its proven track record and innovative technology, Flam now crosses a new frontier by getting into FinTech, Automobile, Banking, and more with mixed reality brand integrations \\u00a0 lined up for the next 15 days and beyond.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Outside its venture into Fintech, Flam continues to expand its footprint within existing sectors.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1653, \"end\": 1660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_technology\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintech\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_technology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Financial_technology\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With new partnerships in F&B and Real Estate in the pipeline, the brand is demonstrating its potential to drive growth for brands across various verticals.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodservice\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"F&B\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodservice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Foodservice\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this journey of expanding reach and influence, Flam remains committed to delivering exceptional mixed-reality experiences that are captivating and produce tangible results.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The partnership with Aditya Birla Capital is a testament to Flam's ability to innovate and adapt, positioning the platform as a frontrunner in shaping the future of advertising.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aditya_Birla_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aditya Birla Capital\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q2422